widgets.title: Queue Managers Status
widgets.nrql: FROM MQObjectStatusSample SELECT latest(status) AS `Queue Manager Status`, latest(channelInitStatus), latest(commandServerStatus) WHERE object = 'QueueManager' FACET name  SINCE 5 minutes ago

widgets.title: Listeners Status
widgets.nrql: FROM MQObjectStatusSample SELECT latest(status) AS `Listener Status`WHERE object = 'Listener' FACET name SINCE 5 minutes ago
